-- Shanghai Shimao Says First-Half Net Income May Increase About Eightfold
-- Bloomberg News
-- 2010-07-22T22:53:00Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-22/shanghai-shimao-says-first-half-net-income-may-increase-about-eightfold.html

          
          
             Shanghai Shimao Co.’s first-half net
income may rise about 700 percent, the company said in a
statement to Shanghai’s stock exchange, without giving a profit
figure.  
